OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showers gradually fading
OL,6,Fto leave a largely dry and bright day,
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells. Chance of a few
OL,8,Flight and well scattered showers
OL,9,Fbreaking out during the afternoon.
OL,10,FBreezy along the coasts. Slightly
OL,11,Fmilder inland than recent days.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny daytime showers soon
OL,14,Ffading this evening to leave a dry
OL,15,Fnight, with some lengthy clear spells.
OL,16,FTurning chilly, with patchy frost in
OL,17,Fprone rural spots, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
